  "description": "Simple mod that adds the unused bubble popping particle and sound.",
  "body": "<br>\n<center>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.moddinglegacy.com/295318538561950008-03-17-2021-1615958915.gif\" alt=\"undefined\" />\n</center>\n<br>\n<center>\n<h1>\nPop\n</h1>\n\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/4DeTbGB8c5\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/223938153260515328.svg?color=7289DA&amp;label=discord&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=FFFFFF&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Modding Legacy Discord Server\" /></a> <a href=\"https://neoforged.net\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/BUILT_WITH-NEOFORGE-d7742f?style=for-the-badge&logo=neoforge&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Built with NeoForge\" /></a>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ModdingLegacy\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/twitter/follow/ModdingLegacy?style=social\" alt=\"Follow us! ModdingLegacy Twitter\" /></a> <a href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/moddinglegacy.com\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/moddinglegacy.com-0285FF?logo=bluesky&logoColor=00&style=social\" alt=\"Follow us! moddinglegacy.com Bluesky\" /></a> <a href=\"https://youtube.com/channel/UCUhDvKdbaKHrKvV5kcKqqiQ\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/youtube/channel/subscribers/UCUhDvKdbaKHrKvV5kcKqqiQ?sub_confirmation=1&style=social&label=@ModdingLegacy\" alt=\"Subscribe to us on YouTube!\" /></a>\n<br><br>\n\nSimple mod that adds the unused bubble popping particle and sound.\n<br><hr />\n</center>\n<br>\n\n<h2>💦 Summary</h2>\nThis is a very lightweight client-side mod that just adds the unused bubble popping particle and sounds from vanilla Minecraft. Why? Because it's cool.<br><br>\n\n<h2>What does this do</h2>\nThis.<br><br>\n\n<br>\n<center>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.moddinglegacy.com/520617755422242633-03-17-2021-1615999048.gif\" alt=\"whatspopping\" />\n</center>\n<br>\n<h2>Configuration</h2>\nThere's an unused popping sound that goes along with it. You can edit the pop-client.toml file to enable this.<br><br>\n\n<br>\n<center>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.moddinglegacy.com/280673968086616594-03-17-2021-1616015549.png\" alt=\"config\" />\n</center>\n<hr />\n<br>\n\n<span><strong>🤚 Support: If you have questions or any issues with our mods, read the FAQ! You can also either <a href=\"https://gitlab.com/groups/modding-legacy/-/issues\">submit an issue on the issue tracker</a>, or come into our Discord server where we can help you!</strong></span>\n<br><br>\n\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/4DeTbGB8c5\"><img src=\"https://discordapp.com/api/guilds/223938153260515328/widget.png?style=banner3\" alt=\"Modding Legacy Discord Server\" /></a>\n<br>",
